variable {Œì : Type u} [Category.{v} Œì]
variable (A : Œì ‚•§ Grpd.{v‚ÇÅ,u‚ÇÅ}) (Œ± : Œì ‚•§ PGrpd.{v‚ÇÅ,u‚ÇÅ}) (h : Œ± ‚ãô PGrpd.forgetToGrpd = A)

/-- `sec` is the universal lift in the following diagram,
  which is a section of `Groupoidal.forget`
             Œ±
  ===== Œì -------Œ±--------------¬¨
 ‚Äñ      ‚Üì sec                   V
 ‚Äñ     ‚à´(A) ----------------> PGrpd
 ‚Äñ      |                        |
